snippet.title: Labyrinth: Immortal Oblivion - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Our steam-page is online now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2203270/Labyrinth_Immortal_Oblivion/

Labyrinth: Immortal Oblivion is a singleplayer, story-driven, dante inspired, horror adventure game from Anti-Wisdom Studios. You'll explore a 3D Horror Maze where you'll solve puzzles and fight powerful monsters to uncover its sinister past. Escape before you too are consumed by this twisted place...

This is the official Teaser Trailer for Labyrinth: Immortal Oblivion.
